<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ881115-0157 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News: Daiwa Securities Co. </HL><SO> </SO><CO> J.DST WNEWS </CO><DATELINE> DAIWA SECURITIES Co.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Robert DeMarco was named senior vice president, financial futures, a newly created post at this Japanese brokerage and investment banking company's Daiwa Securities America unit. He had been responsible for the development of futures and options strategies for use in conjunction with government and mortgage securities at Bear, Stearns andamp; Co. </TEXT></DOC>